{"title":"华尔街的药铺","authors":["杨红风"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的药铺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨红风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老板的药铺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设在华尔街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柜台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆着些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄色的药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色的药……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面表明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专卖给中国人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“民主个人主义者”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾老板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦急地坐着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等人来买，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上的汗往下淌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇着芭蕉扇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他告人说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃上就好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是“友谊关系”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不想买给中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴得很明显"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了半天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一个顾客。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾老板心想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真糟糕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定知道我的密秘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾老板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻起药偷看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄色的药—“侵略”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的药—“侵略”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色的药—“侵略”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九、北平"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}